\f[B]run\-constantly\f[R](1), \f[B]run\-one\-constantly\f[R](1),
\f[B]run\-one\-until\-failure\f[R](1),
\f[B]run\-one\-until\-success\f[R](1), \f[B]run\-until\-failure\f[R](1),
\f[B]run\-until\-success\f[R](1)
.PP
